                <mxCell id="2243" value="Contract CO7: processCampaign()&#xa;Operation: processCampaign()&#xa;Cross Reference: Play Campaign use case&#xa;Pre condition: &#xa;- User is a RegisteredUser&#xa;- User has completed at least 1 puzzle in the campaign&#xa;Post condition:&#xa;- An instance Campaign c was created (instance creation)&#xa;- Progression.mode is set to &quot;Campaign&quot; (attribute modification)&#xa;- c.difficulty is set (attribute modification)&#xa;- c.level is set (attribute modification)&#xa;- An instance of a Pool pl was created (instance creation)&#xa;- c is associated with pl (association formed)&#xa;- An instance of a Puzzle p was created (instance creation)&#xa;- c is associated with p (association formed)&#xa;- p.seed is set to random (att modification)&#xa;Post condition [level completed]:&#xa;- timer is stopped (att modification)&#xa;- c.time is recalculated (att modification)&#xa;- c.level is set to new level (att modifcation)" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;rotatable=0;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="2242">
